        {
            "title": "半日收市︱好淡爭持 恒指半日跌173點報23426點 資源股造好 「ATM」全線跌",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">港股四連跌後於今早出現好淡爭持局面，成交亦略為縮減。近期較被市場忽略的資源股造好，熱門科股則個別發展。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"AP圖片\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/03/20230808_FI_source-ap_港股3.png.webp\">\n<img alt=\"AP圖片\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/03/20230808_FI_source-ap_港股3.png.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">AP圖片</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">恒生指數今早輕微高開16點後便於10天線(最新約為23594點)升與跌百多點的範圍內波動，低位報23417點、跌182點，高位23712點、升112點，半日高低位相差不足300點；恒指中午收報23426點，跌173點或0.74%。</p>\n<!-- slider begin -->\n<div class=\"fancy-slider\">\n<p class=\"fancy-gallery-tips\" style=\"font-weight: bold;font-size: 18px; margin: 0\">點擊看圖輯</p>\n<div class=\"fancy-main\">\n<div class=\"swiper-wrapper\">\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<a class=\"fancy-main__slide\" data-caption=\"AP圖片\" data-fancybox=\"slider-gallery\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/03/20230808_FI_source-ap_港股3.png.webp\">\n<div class=\"fancy-main__image\">\n<img alt=\"AP圖片\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/03/20230808_FI_source-ap_港股3.png.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-main__title bpcategory-special-color\">AP圖片</h3>\n</a>\n</div>\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<a class=\"fancy-main__slide\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：騰訊官網\" data-fancybox=\"slider-gallery\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/768x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/03/20250307_FI_source-web_00700.jpg.webp\">\n<div class=\"fancy-main__image\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：騰訊官網\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/768x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/03/20250307_FI_source-web_00700.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-main__title bpcategory-special-color\">圖片來源：騰訊官網</h3>\n</a>\n</div>\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<a class=\"fancy-main__slide\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：快手網站\" data-fancybox=\"slider-gallery\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2023/07/bplib_20230713-103133_source-web_快手-4_source-web_.jpg.webp\">\n<div class=\"fancy-main__image\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：快手網站\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2023/07/bplib_20230713-103133_source-web_快手-4_source-web_.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-main__title bpcategory-special-color\">圖片來源：快手網站</h3>\n</a>\n</div>\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<a class=\"fancy-main__slide\" data-caption=\"越疆科技官網\" data-fancybox=\"slider-gallery\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/06/Yuejiang.jpg.webp\">\n<div class=\"fancy-main__image\">\n<img alt=\"越疆科技官網\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/06/Yuejiang.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-main__title bpcategory-special-color\">越疆科技官網</h3>\n</a>\n</div>\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<a class=\"fancy-main__slide\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：招商銀行官網影片截圖\" data-fancybox=\"slider-gallery\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2023/07/bplib_20230718-143203_source-web_招商銀行03968-2-官網影片截圖_source-web_.jpg.webp\">\n<div class=\"fancy-main__image\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：招商銀行官網影片截圖\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2023/07/bplib_20230718-143203_source-web_招商銀行03968-2-官網影片截圖_source-web_.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-main__title bpcategory-special-color\">圖片來源：招商銀行官網影片截圖</h3>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"fancy-main__controls\">\n<div class=\"fancy-main__controls-text bpcategory-special-color\">更多相片</div>\n<div class=\"fancy-main__buttons\">\n<div class=\"fancy-main__button __prev fancy-main-prev\" style=\"border-right: 8px solid #996600\"></div>\n<div class=\"rule\"></div>\n<div class=\"fancy-main__button __next fancy-main-next\" style=\"border-left: 8px solid #996600\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"fancy-thumbs\">\n<div class=\"swiper-wrapper\">\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<div class=\"fancy-thumbs__image\">\n<img alt=\"AP圖片\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/03/20230808_FI_source-ap_港股3.png.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-thumbs__title bpcategory-special-color\">AP圖片</h3>\n</div>\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<div class=\"fancy-thumbs__image\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：騰訊官網\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/768x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/03/20250307_FI_source-web_00700.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-thumbs__title bpcategory-special-color\">圖片來源：騰訊官網</h3>\n</div>\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<div class=\"fancy-thumbs__image\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：快手網站\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2023/07/bplib_20230713-103133_source-web_快手-4_source-web_.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-thumbs__title bpcategory-special-color\">圖片來源：快手網站</h3>\n</div>\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<div class=\"fancy-thumbs__image\">\n<img alt=\"越疆科技官網\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/06/Yuejiang.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-thumbs__title bpcategory-special-color\">越疆科技官網</h3>\n</div>\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<div class=\"fancy-thumbs__image\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：招商銀行官網影片截圖\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2023/07/bplib_20230718-143203_source-web_招商銀行03968-2-官網影片截圖_source-web_.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-thumbs__title bpcategory-special-color\">圖片來源：招商銀行官網影片截圖</h3>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<!-- slider end -->\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">恒生科技指數明顯跑輸，半日跌126點或2.17%，報5718點；國企指數跌70點或0.81%，報8611點。主板半日成交1215.36億元，較昨天早市少逾百億元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">即月期指半日跌198點，報23441點，高水14點。科指期貨跌137點，報5727點，高水8點。國指期貨跌70點，報8618點，高水6點。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：騰訊官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/768x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/03/20250307_FI_source-web_00700.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：騰訊官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/768x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/03/20250307_FI_source-web_00700.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：騰訊官網</p>\n</a>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">重磅科股不少繼續調整，「ATM」便全線報跌，當中以騰訊(00700)跌得最少，半日亦跌1.37%，報505元；昨天逆市報升的阿里巴巴(09988)，今早則回吐2.75%，報131.1元；美團(03690)更跌2.85%，報163.5元。上述3隻股份合共拖低恒指122點。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">早前備受追捧的芯片及半導體相關股亦進一步調整，中芯國際(00981)挫4.67%，報50元，在藍籌中排尾二；華虹半導體(01347)跌2.43%，報36.2元；上海復旦(01385)跌4.69%，報27.45元；英諾賽科(02577)跌4.4%，報47.8元。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">至於表現最差藍籌，則是早前炒上的快手(01024)，半日跌5.09%，報62.5元。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：快手網站\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2023/07/bplib_20230713-103133_source-web_快手-4_source-web_.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：快手網站\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2023/07/bplib_20230713-103133_source-web_快手-4_source-web_.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：快手網站</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">當然，也有熱門科股受捧。小米(01810)便先跌後反彈，升0.29%，報52.2元；早前因智駕概念屢創新高的比亞迪(01211)，更漲1.3%，報359.6元。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">最新發布人形機械人的越疆(02432)昨天破頂後，今日再飆22.15%，報63.15元；專注於自動駕駛計算芯片的黑芝麻智能(02533)亦升4.9%，報25.7元。不過，地平線機械人(09660)則先升後挫，倒跌3.93%，報8.06元。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"越疆科技官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/06/Yuejiang.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"越疆科技官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/06/Yuejiang.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">越疆科技官網</p>\n</a>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">資源股追落後，今早藍籌升幅榜頭5位有3隻是資源股，表現最佳的是中國神華(01088)，升2.09%，報31.8元；紫金礦業(02899)是季軍，半日升1.74%，報16.36元；中海油(00883)則排第4名，漲1.69%，報18.06元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">內銀股偏強，招商銀行(03968)升1.89%，報48.65元，是表現次佳藍籌；農業銀行(01288)升1.03%，報4.93元。兩大重磅金融股則個別發展，滙控(00005)升0.88%，報85.8元；明天派成績表的友邦(01299)卻要跌1.1%，報63.1元。</p>\n\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：招商銀行官網影片截圖\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2023/07/bplib_20230718-143203_source-web_招商銀行03968-2-官網影片截圖_source-web_.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：招商銀行官網影片截圖\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2023/07/bplib_20230718-143203_source-web_招商銀行03968-2-官網影片截圖_source-web_.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：招商銀行官網影片截圖</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">本地地產股有反彈，領展(00823)升1.63%，報37.45元，創3個月新高；九龍倉置業(01997)回升1.02%，報19.84元。新世界發展(00017)據報獲內地4大國有商業銀行在監管機構敦促下提供信貸支持，今早股價升1.74%，報5.27元；同屬鄭氏家族旗下的周大福(01929)也升1.2%，報9.28元。</p>\n</div>",
